{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4d6b6673e6","title":"毛泽东会见古巴党政代表团时的谈话（摘录）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1cc834dc9b","index":0,"year":1964,"month":10,"day":16,"articleId":"4d6b6673e6"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"84146d0cbf","type":"title","text":"会见古巴党政代表团时的谈话（摘录）","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4d6b6673e6"},{"id":"1796cc7c4a","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4d6b6673e6"},{"id":"42d39e779b","type":"paragraph","text":"我这个人老早就讲了，要为劳动人民，要为工农兵，讲了二十几年。可是以后没有去抓。只要你不去抓，他就照例不动。不为工农兵服务，不为社会主义服务，而是为资本主义、为封建主义服务。资产阶级掌握文化、艺术、教育、学术，可顽固哪！尽是他们的人，我们的人很少。这种情况再过几年可能会在你们国家出现。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4d6b6673e6"}],"page":{"id":"34171b2149","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4d6b6673e6","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}